  "texts": [
    "This study adopted a modified PRISMA diagram tailored to align with the bibliometric analysis approach, thereby elucidating the research framework and procedures.",
    "This customized diagram was proposed by Ahmi (2021).",
    "Figure 1 provides a comprehensive illustration of this approach, commencing with the delineation of the research topic, the identification of search keywords and the definition of the scope and coverage based on specific criteria, culminating in the determination of the total number of documents earmarked for analysis within the bibliometric study.",
    "In this research, the VOSviewer application was pivotal in identifying recurrent keywords and categorizing thematic groupings within the body of literature on GeoGebra.",
    "VOSviewer is a software tool extensively used in bibliometric analysis to visualize and examine bibliographic data (van Eck & Waltman, 2010)."
  ]
}